---
import { XCircle, CheckCircle2 } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section class="comparison-5 section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2 class="section-title">Kenapa Harus Pakai Sistem?</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Lihat perbedaan hasil kerja manual vs pakai Clipcash AI.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-table">
      <div class="comp-col manual">
        <h3>Kerja Manual (Ribet)</h3>
        <div class="comp-list">
          <div class="comp-item">
            <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
            <span>Bingung mulai dari mana, tutorial random pusing.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
            <span>Edit video habisin 1-3 jam, capek duluan.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
            <span>Gak tau formula viral, video sepi penonton.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
            <span>Sering berhenti di tengah jalan karena gak ada arah.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comp-col ai">
        <div class="badge-best">REKOMENDASI</div>
        <h3>Pakai Clipcash (Gampang)</h3>
        <div class="comp-list">
          <div class="comp-item">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
            <span>Ada SOP mudah diikuti dari nol sampai cuan.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
            <span>Tinggal copas link, AI yang proses videonya.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
            <span>Ada formula retention: hook & timing viral.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="comp-item">
            <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
            <span>Ada checklist harian biar lo tetap konsisten.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .comparison-5 {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: #0F0F0F;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .comp-col {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 24px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .manual { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02); }
  
  .ai { 
    background: rgba(250, 176, 5, 0.05); 
    border-color: rgba(250, 176, 5, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
  }

  .badge-best {
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: #FAB005;
    color: #0F0F0F;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .comp-col h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .comp-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .comp-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .comp-item span {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .text-red { color: #ff4b4b; }
  .text-green { color: #52BD94; }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .comparison-table { flex-direction: column; }
  }
</style>
